{"lemma":"صَيارِفَةُ","slug":"صَيارِفَةُ","root":"ص.ر.ف","root_slug":"ص-ر-ف","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-ر-ف","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n24237"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%8E%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of صَيْرَفِيّ (ṣayrafiyy)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/sˤa.jaː.ri.fa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n24237","headword_ar":"صَيْرَفِىٌّ","root":"Srf","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sar~aAfN","text_ar":"صَرَّافٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, O, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sar~aAfu","text_ar":"صَرَّافُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daraAhima","text_ar":"دَرَاهِمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SayorafN","text_ar":"صَيْرَفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, Msb, K,) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A money-changer;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, Msb, TA;) except that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sar~aAfN","text_ar":"صَرَّافٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"has an intensive signification [app. as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a skilful money-changer,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and hence it is often used in the present day as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a banker"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Msb:) all are applied to him"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who knows and distinguishes the relative excellence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"superiority, of pieces of money:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) these appellations are from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmuSaArafapu","text_ar":"المُصَارَفَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,) or from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~aSar~ufu","text_ar":"التَّصَرُّفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) or from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SarofN","text_ar":"صَرْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning “ excellence, ” or “ superiority, ” of one dirhem [or deenár] over another, (Mgh, and Msb on the authority of IF in relation to the first,) because such as excels, or is superior, is turned aside from the deficient: (Mgh:) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SayaArifapN","text_ar":"صَيَارِفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, O, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SayaArifu","text_ar":"صَيَارِفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SayaAriyfu","text_ar":"صَيَارِيفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", this last occurring in poetry, (S, M, O, K,) by poetic license, for the sake of the measure. (S, O.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SayorafN","text_ar":"صَيْرَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","M","O","Msb","K","Mgh"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}